reviewText: Do not Remember ever watching this on Saturday morning cartoons back in 1973. Or anytime in the 1970s for that matter. Never had No idea until watching this vhs tape and my other one,that it even had anything to do with the partridge family tv show cartoon format. wouldn't buy it again IF tape wore out. NO where near as good as Scooby doo or Josie and the pussycats,Not even Close!
